# Class: obo:GENEPIO_0002137 (breadth of coverage)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000111 obo:GENEPIO_0002137 "breadth of coverage")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000112 obo:GENEPIO_0002137 "Eighty percent of the reference genome was covered by sequence fragments with a coverage depth of 4X; therefore, the breadth of coverage was 80% (4:5).")
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000114 obo:GENEPIO_0002137 obo:IAO_0000122)
AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:GENEPIO_0002137 "A data item which is the amount of a reference sequence covered by a sequence of interest.")
